        id - id of the complaint, only set when retrieved from the server
        type - type of complaint
        description - description of the complaint
        timestamp - when the complaint was sent, set on the server
        sender_ip - ip of the complainer
        location - location of the complaint
        name - name of user who sent the complaint
        resolved - whether the complaint has been resolved yet, set to false when initially created
